                        </div>
                        <div class="trail-feature">
                            <span class="feature-icon">🌫️</span>
                            <span class="feature-text">Ridge</span>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="adventure-badge">
                    <i class="fas fa-heart"></i>
                    <span>A must-have trip on your list!! Everyone must have Pitue Gro waterfall trip on their list</span>
