                <h3>🌿 Sae Palata Waterfall - Limestone waterfall of Umphang</h3>
                <p class="highlight">A beautiful and private waterfall in Umphang Wildlife Sanctuary</p>

                <div class="info-grid">
                    <div class="info-item">
