                <p class="description">Sae Palata Waterfall is a medium-sized limestone waterfall with a width of approximately 10 meters and a height of approximately 50 meters. The stream flows down along tiered stone formations, creating a beautiful and gentle cascade. Located in Umphang Wildlife Sanctuary and close to a Karen village.</p>

