                <p class="description">Khota Waterfall is formed from Huay Klot To Stream like Thi Lo Su Waterfall, but is located in the lower section of Thi Lo Su Waterfall, before flowing into the Mae Klong River. The characteristics of the stream at Khota Waterfall flow down along limestone tiers, forming more than 10 tiers, which is very beautiful.</p>

