                <button onclick="toggleTourItinerary(4)" class="btn" style="width: 100%; padding: 0.75rem; background: #F3F4F6; color: #1A1A1A; border: 2px solid #E5E7EB; border-radius: 12px; font-size: 0.9rem; font-weight: 600; cursor: pointer; transition: all 0.3s; margin-top: 0.75rem;">📋 View Itinerary</button>
                <button onclick="openTourBookingModal(4)" class="btn btn-primary" style="width: 100%; padding: 1.3rem; background: #FFD700; color: #000000; border: 2px solid #FFD700; border-radius: 20px; font-size: 0.76rem; font-weight: 700; cursor: pointer; transition: all 0.3s; margin-top: 0.75rem;">📝 Book This Tour</button>
            </div>

            <!-- Tour 5: Doi Hua Mot -->
            <div class="tour-card">
                <span class="tour-card-badge">🏔️</span>
                <h4 class="tour-card-title">🏔️ Doi Hua Mot</h4>
                <p class="tour-card-route">Sea of mist view at Doi Hua Mot summit</p>
                <div class="tour-card-price" id="tour5-price">฿1,000 <span>/Group (1-5 People)</span></div>
                <p style="font-size: 0.92rem; color: var(--gray); margin-top: 0.5rem;">6-10 People: ฿1,500</p>
                <div class="form-group" style="margin-top: 1rem;">
                    <label style="font-size: 0.92rem; color: var(--dark-gray); font-weight: 600;">Number of People</label>
                    <select id="tour5-people" onchange="updateTourPrice(5)" style="width: 100%; padding: 0.75rem; border: 2px solid var(--light-gray); border-radius: 10px; font-size: 1.03rem;">
                        <option value="1">1 People</option>
                        <option value="2">2 People</option>
                        <option value="3">3 People</option>
                        <option value="4">4 People</option>
                        <option value="5" selected>5 People</option>
                        <option value="6">6 People</option>
                        <option value="7">7 People</option>
                        <option value="8">8 People</option>
                        <option value="9">9 People</option>
                        <option value="10">10 People</option>
                    </select>
                </div>
                <div class="tour-total-price" id="tour5-total" style="margin-top: 0.75rem; padding: 0.75rem; background: var(--yellow-light); border-radius: 10px; text-align: center;">
                    <span style="font-size: 0.92rem; color: var(--dark-gray);">PriceTotal: </span>
                    <span style="font-size: 0.91rem; font-weight: 800; color: var(--charcoal);">฿1,000</span>
                </div>
                <button onclick="toggleTourItinerary(5)" class="btn" style="width: 100%; padding: 0.75rem; background: #F3F4F6; color: #1A1A1A; border: 2px solid #E5E7EB; border-radius: 12px; font-size: 0.9rem; font-weight: 600; cursor: pointer; transition: all 0.3s; margin-top: 0.75rem;">📋 View Itinerary</button>
                <button onclick="openTourBookingModal(5)" class="btn btn-primary" style="width: 100%; padding: 1.3rem; background: #FFD700; color: #000000; border: 2px solid #FFD700; border-radius: 20px; font-size: 0.76rem; font-weight: 700; cursor: pointer; transition: all 0.3s; margin-top: 0.75rem;">📝 Book This Tour</button>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Tour Itinerary Modals -->
    <div id="tourItineraryModal1" class="tour-itinerary-modal" style="display: none;">
        <div class="tour-itinerary-content">
            <div class="tour-itinerary-header">
                <h3>🌿 Thi Lo Su Waterfall Tour Itinerary</h3>
                <button class="itinerary-close" onclick="toggleTourItinerary(1)">×</button>
            </div>
            <div class="tour-itinerary-body">
                <table class="itinerary-table">
                    <tr><td class="time">05:30 AM</td><td>A vehicle will pick you up for a sunrise experience and sea-of-mist photography at a scenic viewpoint.</td></tr>
                    <tr><td class="time">07:45 – 08:30 AM</td><td>Return to the resort to relax and prepare for the next activity.</td></tr>
                    <tr><td class="time">08:30 AM</td><td>Depart from the resort by vehicle to the boat pier.</td></tr>
                    <tr><td class="time">08:45 AM</td><td>Enjoy a scenic boat ride along the refreshing natural stream. Along the way you will pass: Takhobi Hot Spring, Thi Lo Cho Waterfall, Rainbow Waterfall, Pha Luead Cliff, Hin Tor Rock formations. You will also experience small fun rapids during the rafting journey. Local villagers may offer handmade snacks and souvenirs along the river.</td></tr>
                    <tr><td class="time">12:00 PM</td><td>Disembark from the boat and continue the journey by 4×4 vehicle into the Thi Lo Su Waterfall area.</td></tr>
                    <tr><td class="time">01:00 PM</td><td>Lunch will be served.</td></tr>
                    <tr><td class="time">01:30 PM</td><td>Walk to the magnificent Thi Lo Su Waterfall.</td></tr>
                    <tr><td class="time">01:30 – 03:00 PM</td><td>Enjoy exploring the waterfall and surrounding nature at your leisure.</td></tr>
                    <tr><td class="time">03:00 – 04:00 PM</td><td>Return journey from the waterfall.</td></tr>
                    <tr><td class="time">04:00 PM</td><td>Arrive back at the resort and relax at your own leisure.</td></tr>
                </table>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div id="tourItineraryModal2" class="tour-itinerary-modal" style="display: none;">
        <div class="tour-itinerary-content">
            <div class="tour-itinerary-header">
                <h3>🌿 Thi Lo Su – Koh Tha Waterfall Tour Itinerary</h3>
                <button class="itinerary-close" onclick="toggleTourItinerary(2)">×</button>
            </div>
            <div class="tour-itinerary-body">
                <table class="itinerary-table">
                    <tr><td class="time">05:30 AM</td><td>Pickup from the resort for a sunrise and sea-of-mist photography experience at a panoramic viewpoint.</td></tr>
                    <tr><td class="time">07:45 – 08:30 AM</td><td>Return to the resort for a short rest before the boat trip.</td></tr>
                    <tr><td class="time">08:30 AM</td><td>Transfer by vehicle from the resort to the boat pier.</td></tr>
                    <tr><td class="time">08:45 AM</td><td>Begin a peaceful boat journey along the cool natural river. During the ride you will pass: Takhobi Hot Spring, Thi Lo Cho Waterfall, Rainbow Waterfall, Pha Luead Cliff, Hin Tor Rock formations. Guests will also enjoy light rapids rafting and may purchase local products from villagers along the riverbanks.</td></tr>
                    <tr><td class="time">11:00 AM</td><td>Leave the boat and continue by 4×4 vehicle into the Thi Lo Su National Park area.</td></tr>
                    <tr><td class="time">12:00 PM</td><td>Lunch break.</td></tr>
                    <tr><td class="time">12:30 PM</td><td>Walk to visit the breathtaking Thi Lo Su Waterfall.</td></tr>
                    <tr><td class="time">12:30 – 02:00 PM</td><td>Free time to explore and relax at the waterfall.</td></tr>
                    <tr><td class="time">02:00 – 02:30 PM</td><td>Travel onward to Koh Tha Waterfall.</td></tr>
                    <tr><td class="time">02:30 – 03:30 PM</td><td>Enjoy swimming, relaxing, and sightseeing at Koh Tha Waterfall.</td></tr>
                    <tr><td class="time">03:30 PM</td><td>Depart from the waterfalls and begin the return journey.</td></tr>
                    <tr><td class="time">05:00 PM</td><td>Arrive back at the resort. Free time to relax.</td></tr>
                </table>
                <p style="margin-top: 1rem; padding: 0.75rem; background: #FEF3C7; border-radius: 8px; color: #92400E; font-size: 0.9rem; text-align: center;">⚠️ Note: Joytrip does not include Doi Hua Mot</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div id="tourItineraryModal3" class="tour-itinerary-modal" style="display: none;">
        <div class="tour-itinerary-content">
            <div class="tour-itinerary-header">
                <h3>🚙 4x4 Vehicle Thi Lo Su Tour</h3>
                <button class="itinerary-close" onclick="toggleTourItinerary(3)">×</button>
            </div>
            <div class="tour-itinerary-body">
