                    <tr><td class="time">08:00 AM</td><td>Resort vehicle pickup from your accommodation</td></tr>
                    <tr><td class="time">08:30 AM</td><td>Depart by 4x4 vehicle to Thi Lo Su Waterfall</td></tr>
                    <tr><td class="time">10:00 AM</td><td>Stop for scenic views and nature photography</td></tr>
                    <tr><td class="time">11:30 AM</td><td>Arrive at Thi Lo Su Waterfall</td></tr>
                    <tr><td class="time">11:30 – 01:00 PM</td><td>Explore and relax at the waterfall</td></tr>
                    <tr><td class="time">01:00 PM</td><td>Lunch break (included in tour)</td></tr>
                    <tr><td class="time">01:30 – 03:00 PM</td><td>Continue exploring or relax at your leisure</td></tr>
